# MRL Product Combo Manager Structure

## Component Domains
```
src/components/
├── ui/           # Reusable primitives
│   ├── CopyableCell.tsx
│   ├── SortButton.tsx
│   ├── ResizableTableContainer.tsx
│   └── ScrapeHero.tsx
├── upload/       # File upload components
│   ├── CsvDropZone.tsx
│   └── HtmlDropZone.tsx
├── product/      # Product display/editing
│   ├── ProductRowCard/    # Folder for complex component
│   ├── ProductRowCard.tsx
│   ├── ProductImageWithDots.tsx
│   ├── VisualizationSection.tsx
│   └── ImageCard.tsx
├── layout/       # App layout
│   ├── Sidebar.tsx
│   ├── SidebarNav.tsx
│   ├── MainContent.tsx
│   └── ProcessSidebar.tsx
└── crosssell/    # Crosssell feature
    └── SortableCrossSellRow.tsx
```

