```
src/app/
├── edit-combo/
│   ├── page.tsx           # Main page (~150 lines)
│   ├── _components/       # Page-specific components
│   │   ├── AddMainProductModal.tsx
│   │   ├── ImportDataModal.tsx
│   │   ├── UpdateSheetModal.tsx
│   │   └── index.ts
│   └── _hooks/
│       └── useEditComboPage.ts
├── crosssell/
│   ├── page.tsx
│   ├── settings/page.tsx
│   └── _hooks/
│       └── useCrosssellPage.ts
├── view-production/page.tsx
├── settings/page.tsx
└── api/                   # API routes
    ├── products/
    ├── upload/
    └── crosssell/
```

## Library Structure
```
src/lib/
├── client/               # Client-side only
│   ├── services/         # API calls, external integrations
│   │   ├── product-service.ts
│   │   ├── csv-export-service.ts
│   │   ├── html-export-service.ts
│   │   ├── google-sheets-service.ts
│   │   └── import-service.ts
│   ├── utils/            # Pure functions, parsers
│   │   └── js-parser.ts
│   ├── context/          # React contexts
│   └── hooks/            # Shared hooks
├── server/               # Server-side only
└── shared/               # Both client & server
    └── utils/
```

## Rules
1. **New component**: Add to existing domain folder if related
2. **New feature**: Create new domain folder
3. **Each domain**: MUST have `index.ts` barrel export
4. **Page > 200 lines**: Extract to `_hooks/`
5. **Component > 300 lines**: Split into sub-components
6. **Function used 2+ places**: Move to services/utils
